01:39:50,200 --> 01:39:53,237
You know, there's a back door
out if you, you know,
wanna be a little more s--

1326
01:39:53,360 --> 01:39:56,750
This check is bullshit, Tom.

1327
01:39:56,880 --> 01:40:01,192
What'd you think,
I'm just gonna waltz outta here,
you lying motherfucker? Huh?

1328
01:40:01,320 --> 01:40:06,348
Let you make a phone call,
have half the cops in New York
waitin' for me while I cash this thing?

1329
01:40:06,480 --> 01:40:08,277
- You can't lie to me.
- Look--

1330
01:40:08,400 --> 01:40:10,550
Shut your mouth.

1331
01:40:12,840 --> 01:40:14,637
Fuck!

1332
01:40:25,000 --> 01:40:28,595
You know who I am.
Now you sit down.

1333
01:40:30,280 --> 01:40:33,716
Everybody was gonna make out fine.

1334
01:40:33,840 --> 01:40:36,195
But you had to go
and put it together...

1335
01:40:36,320 --> 01:40:41,553
and now we got
a little problem here, don't we?

1336
01:40:41,680 --> 01:40:44,035
Tell me that part again about
why you didn't pay the ransom.

1337
01:40:44,160 --> 01:40:46,037
- I think we can do something here--
- Say it!

1338
01:40:46,160 --> 01:40:48,469
You were dealing with what?

1339
01:40:50,560 --> 01:40:54,872
- You had my son.
- You have no idea what
human garbage is, motherfucker.

1340
01:40:55,000 --> 01:40:57,878
Do you know what the fuck you're
talking about? No, I don't think you do.

1341
01:40:58,000 --> 01:41:02,073
'Cause look where you fuckin' live, man.
Look at the airline man here.

1342
01:41:02,200 --> 01:41:05,909
This fucker won't pay one cent
to save his only kid.

1343
01:41:06,040 --> 01:41:09,350
- It wasn't gonna get him back, was it?
- Hey, did you read the papers? Huh?

1344
01:41:09,480 --> 01:41:11,277
Did you see the TV?

1345
01:41:11,400 --> 01:41:14,597
I took a bullet.
I risked my life to save your kid.

1346
01:41:14,720 --> 01:41:18,110
