try to fuck me out of my money. Huh?

1347
01:41:18,240 --> 01:41:20,993
- What's over here?
- Where are you going?
- Where's Mommy and Junior?

1348
01:41:21,120 --> 01:41:24,032
- Now I'll pay. Now.
- Oh, yeah.

1349
01:41:24,160 --> 01:41:27,470
You're gonna pay, all right.
Right now.

1350
01:41:27,600 --> 01:41:30,751
Do you have an account I can wire
the money to? I mean, you got to have
been all set up for this, right?

1351
01:41:30,880 --> 01:41:35,158
I mean, you're not dumb. You and me,
we go right now to my bank...

1352
01:41:35,280 --> 01:41:37,157
and we wire the money
from my account to yours.

1353
01:41:37,280 --> 01:41:39,396
Just the push of a button.
Just like that.

1354
01:41:39,520 --> 01:41:44,036
We'll just go down to the bank
and get it done.

1355
01:41:44,160 --> 01:41:46,913
Pick up the phone.
Wire it from here.

1356
01:41:49,680 --> 01:41:53,150
Uh, no, we'll go to the bank
and do it.

1357
01:41:53,280 --> 01:41:57,478
And you'll get the money and all I want
in return is you out of this house now.

1358
01:42:00,720 --> 01:42:03,837
Hey. You do not call the shots.

1359
01:42:03,960 --> 01:42:08,272
Well, then, you just go ahead
and kill me right here and now,
you son of a bitch.

1360
01:42:08,400 --> 01:42:11,551
You fuck! Fuck you!
I'm not pickin' up that phone.

1361
01:42:11,680 --> 01:42:14,638
You got that?
I'm not pickin' it up.

1362
01:42:14,760 --> 01:42:18,514
Look, uh, you can kill me.
Go ahead. Kill me. Just kill us.

1363
01:42:18,640 --> 01:42:21,108
Let us live. Doesn't matter.
Any way you cut it, you're on the run.

1364
01:42:21,240 --> 01:42:24,312
Now, you can come with me to the bank
and be on the run with $4 million...

1365
01:42:24,440 --> 01:42:28,069
or you can just start shootin'
and be on the run with whatever
you got in your wallet.

1366
01:42:28,200 --> 01:42:29,997
It's up to you.

1367
01:42:30,120 --> 01:42:34,318
Come on, Jimmy. Let's go to the bank.
Oh, Jesus Christ.

1368
01:42:34,440 --> 01:42:38,274
I got what I want.
Bottom line: I got my son back.

1369
01:42:38,400 --> 01:42:40,516
And you d-- you delivered him.

1370
01:42:40,640 --> 01:42:44,838
I got my own plane. I can fly you out
of here myself anywhere you wanna go.

1371
01:42:44,960 --> 01:42:49,238
You can still win this thing.
Think. You can still win.

1372
01:43:07,040 --> 01:43:09,110
We do what you say.
We go to the bank.

1373
01:43:09,240 --> 01:43:14,678
If anything goes wrong, you're gonna
turn around and I'll be gone.

1374
01:43:14,800 --> 01:43:17,155
Okay? And if that happens...

1375
01:43:17,280 --> 01:43:19,236
from this day on...

1376
01:43:19,360 --> 01:43:22,352
any time your kid leaves
this house to go to school...

1377
01:43:22,480 --> 01:43:26,109
go play, see a friend...

1378
01:43:26,240 --> 01:43:29,312
to buy a fuckin' comic book,
you're gonna have to ask yourself:

1379
01:43:31,240 --> 01:43:33,674
Is today...

1380
01:43:33,800 --> 01:43:36,189
Jimmy Shaker day?

1381
01:43:36,320 --> 01:43:38,959
I got to him once.

1382
01:43:39,080 --> 01:43:41,435
I'll get him again.

1383
01:43:41,560 --> 01:43:44,233
And when I do...

1384
01:43:44,360 --> 01:43:47,955
I'm not gonna want money any more.

1385
01:43:48,080 --> 01:43:50,548
Do we understand each other?

1386
01:43:50,680 --> 01:43:51,954
Sure.

1387
01:44:10,800 --> 01:44:12,199
That's from Maris.

1388
01:44:19,600 --> 01:44:21,397
Call the airport.

1389
01:44:27,320 --> 01:44:29,276
Where are we goin'?

1390
01:44:29,400 --> 01:44:31,709
Mexico. Guadalajara.

1391
01:44:36,240 --> 01:44:41,360
David, this is Tom. Uh, fuel up the jet.
I'm going to Guadalajara.

1392
01:44:41,480 --> 01:44:44,517
Yeah, well, something came up.
I'm on my way to the bank now.

1393
01:44:46,880 --> 01:44:48,836
- Is the kidnapper with you?
- Absolutely.

1394
01:44:51,200 --> 01:44:54,078
I'll explain everything later.
Give Katie a call. Bye.

1395
01:44:56,080 --> 01:44:57,877
Antone, get me the Mullen house.

1396
01:44:58,000 --> 01:45:00,116
Sean, what's the matter, honey?

1397
01:45:01,600 --> 01:45:03,636
Come here.

1398
01:45:05,440 --> 01:45:07,715
Taxi! Taxi!

1399
01:45:11,680 --> 01:45:13,477
Stay on my right.

1400
01:45:15,320 --> 01:45:17,470
What are you guys doin'?
You can't park there.

1401
01:45:17,600 --> 01:45:19,716
Oh, we're just goin'
to the bank. Five minutes.

1402
01:45:21,640 --> 01:45:23,710
- Shaker?
- Yeah.

1403
01:45:26,400 --> 01:45:28,197
- How you doin', Jimmy?
- How are ya?

1404
01:45:28,320 --> 01:45:30,470
- Nice to meet you.
- Yeah? You too.

1405
01:45:30,600 --> 01:45:32,670
- How you doin', Mr Mullen?
Good to meet you.
- Hey.

1406
01:45:32,800 --> 01:45:35,189
Just wanna shake your hand, boss.
You made us proud.

1407
01:45:35,320 --> 01:45:37,117
- Well, you know, just doin' the job.
- Yeah.

1408
01:45:37,240 --> 01:45:40,038
What do you think
of this guy, Mr Mullen?

1409
01:45:40,160 --> 01:45:42,390
- Well, what can I say? He's the man.
- Yeah!

1410
01:45:42,520 --> 01:45:44,909
- Okay, guys, uh, take it easy.
- Later, Jimbo.
- Okay.

1411
01:45:45,040 --> 01:45:47,315
- You guys take it easy now.
- All right.
- You guys not gonna be long, right?

1412
01:45:47,440 --> 01:45:49,795
- No, just five minutes.
- No, no, no.
- No problem.

1413
01:45:56,640 --> 01:45:59,200
Mr Mullen,
what a pleasant surprise.

1414
01:45:59,320 --> 01:46:02,278
Welcome.

1415
01:46:02,400 --> 01:46:06,075
- Uh, have I still got any money
in this bank? I have to do
some business with Mr Shaker here.
- Yes.

1416
01:46:06,200 --> 01:46:08,839
- This is Michael.
- Mr Shaker, of course. Right this way.

1417
01:46:16,960 --> 01:46:21,431
Terrific. Okay, that's enough.
Let's get this man his money.

1418
01:46:21,560 --> 01:46:23,312
- Thanks very much.
- No, not a problem.

1419
01:46:23,440 --> 01:46:26,716
All units in the 22,
