1422
01:46:33,680 --> 01:46:35,716
Subject is an armed
New York City detective.

1423
01:46:35,840 --> 01:46:39,071
Just push enter and it's yours.

1424
01:46:39,200 --> 01:46:41,077
Four million.

1425
01:46:48,320 --> 01:46:49,912
Congratulations.

1426
01:46:50,040 --> 01:46:53,316
Yeah, thanks. Okay.

1427
01:47:00,160 --> 01:47:01,957
Hey, Shaker.

1428
01:47:02,080 --> 01:47:04,310
What's goin' on?
