1443
01:49:32,680 --> 01:49:34,557
Put the gun down.

1444
01:49:34,680 --> 01:49:36,477
- Drop the gun!
- Come on. Walk toward me.

1445
01:49:36,600 --> 01:49:38,875
- Tom, don't do nothin' stupid.
- Put down the gun now!

1446
01:49:39,000 --> 01:49:41,389
- Put the gun down, Tom!
- Drop it!

1447
01:49:45,440 --> 01:49:48,910
On the ground, Shaker!
On the ground!

1448
01:49:49,040 --> 01:49:52,350
- Tom, put the gun down now!
- Down!

1449
01:49:52,480 --> 01:49:55,074
Stay right there!
Now, don't move!

1450
01:49:55,200 --> 01:49:57,316
Put the gun down.

1451
01:49:57,440 --> 01:49:59,715
That's right. Now, back off, Tom.
